{"tid":503836,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【康宏爭權】康宏：入稟高院控告曹貴子、王利民、郭曉群等28人","createTime":"2017-12-19T09:34:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-19T10:02:42.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b88975ea60114ac07053ecae8f23bcfd9656827d","tid":503836,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T09:34:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171219/large/1513658786_a16a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171219%2Flarge%2F1513658786_a16a.jpg&h=9b312ab8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171219/large/1513659635_af70.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171219%2Flarge%2F1513659635_af70.jpg&h=ab6f4dc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【新增影片】康宏環球（1019）與兩間附屬公司就涉嫌被人不當轉移公司資金，導致該公司出現重大財務損失及損害一事，在高等法院向28名被告人展開法律行動追討損失，控告有關人士嚴重違反授信責任，當中包括現遭停職的正副主席王利民、馮雪心及執董曹貴子、主要股東郭曉群等人，知名財經分析員康證有限公司董事黃敏碩、公關公司PR Asia董事總經理凌冠華亦在28名被告當中。<br />\n<br />\n入稟狀提到康宏環球作出的指控，詳情可瀏覽相關新聞 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2BuyfrR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2BuyfrR&d=B%2Bw2zJwXHmCdvCVYd%2B%2FppQIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=5da13565\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2BuyfrR</a><br />\n康宏表示，訴訟由康宏提出，針對第一被告人曹貴子、以及上述公司的指定董事、相關問題循環融資協議的潛在參與者，以及現時持有獲不當分配股權的人士。康宏指將會繼續調查事件，其他監管及執法部門亦正進行調查，不排除未來會加入其他被告人及申索。<br />\n康宏將繼續與會計及法律專業團隊緊密合作，追討其應有權益，包括被不當轉移的公司資金。同時，公司會繼續協助有關當局進行相關調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171219/57600622\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171219%2F57600622&d=B%2Bw2zJwXHmCdvCVYd%2B%2FppQIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=11938901\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171219%2F57600622&h=46cf1232\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171219/57600622</a>"},{"pid":"29cc5b402a0f0185c2e301404cb70fe8a11a2a67","tid":503836,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T09:39:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f2f38a7e393a31a2882f089bdc24fcc64d9d0f5","tid":503836,"uid":119384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T09:59:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n抵撚死喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d26bf17503288419e315f4d2f6fcf8c35e976dac","tid":503836,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T10:02:42.000Z","msg":"呢隻冚家剷股16年買過2次執咗支煙頭，之後再冇買過 <br />\n<br />\n爆就啱啦"}]}